        {
            "title": "李寧上季銷售點流水按年錄中單位數下降",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">李寧(02331)公布第3季最新運營狀況，其中李寧銷售點(不包括李寧YOUNG)於整個平台的零售流水，按年錄中單位數下降。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"李寧官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/02331-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"李寧官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/02331-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">李寧官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">就渠道而言，線下渠道(包括零售及批發)期內錄得高單位數下降，其中零售(直接經營)渠道錄得中單位數下降，批發(特許經銷商)渠道錄得高單位數下降；電子商務虛擬店舖業務，則錄得高單位數增長。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至9月底時，於中國的李寧銷售點數量(不包括李寧YOUNG)共計6132個，單季淨增加33個，年初迄今淨增加15個。在淨增加的15個銷點售中，零售業務淨減少46個，批發業務淨增加61個。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">於中國的李寧YOUNG銷售點數量共計1480個，單季淨增加45個，年初迄今淨增加12個。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15367659-%e6%9d%8e%e5%af%a7%e4%b8%8a%e5%ad%a3%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e9%bb%9e%e6%b5%81%e6%b0%b4%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%8c%84%e4%b8%ad%e5%96%ae%e4%bd%8d%e6%95%b8%e4%b8%8b%e9%99%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20231025_FI_source-web_02331.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 12:25:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市︱升幅略縮 恒指升154點報26122點 重磅科股互有升跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">憧憬中美貿易關係有望進一步緩和，外圍股市造好，港股今早亦重越二萬六並企穩此水平之上作半日結，只是升幅略為縮減。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240801_FI_source-ap_US_China-704.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240801_FI_source-ap_US_China-704.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早甫開市即收復26000點及50天線(最新約為25957點)，開升209點報26177點，初段升幅曾擴大至271點，半日高位達26239點，其後升幅反幅收窄，但早市全程均能企穩於26000點以上，低位26065點時仍升97點；恒指中午收報26122點，升154點或0.59%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240801_FI_source-ap_US_China-704.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240801_FI_source-ap_US_China-704.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240826_FI_source-web_03690-GW-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240826_FI_source-web_03690-GW-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：美團官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：普拉達2023年度年報\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240730_FI_source-web_01913-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：普拉達2023年度年報\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240730_FI_source-web_01913-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：普拉達2023年度年報</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240801_FI_source-ap_US_China-704.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240826_FI_source-web_03690-GW-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：美團官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：普拉達2023年度年報\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240730_FI_source-web_01913-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：普拉達2023年度年報</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數跑贏大市，半日升72點或1.22%，報6024點；國企指數升42點或0.46%，報9343點。主板半日成交1229.3億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日升180點，報26137點，高水15點。科指期貨升71點，報6031點，高水7點。國指期貨升59點，報9657點，高水11點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科股個別發展，中芯國際(00981)重登藍籌升幅榜首，半日漲5.54%，報78.15元，為恒指提供29點進賬，半日成交65.62億元。華虹半導體(01347)更飆11.59%，報80.85元，交投45.76億元，與中芯雙雙躋身主板成交額三甲之列。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">成交最大主板股份是阿里巴巴(09988)，半日交投72.72億元，股價亦跑贏大市，收升2.07%，報168元，是為恒指提供最大點數升幅貢獻的股份，單一股份已令恒指升逾51點。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「ATMXJ」其餘4位成員卻升少跌多，只有騰訊(00700)尚能升0.4%，報635.5元。小米(01810)則跌0.98%，報46.28元；京東(09618)也回吐0.31%，報128.3元；市傳美團(03690)或快落實發行90億至100億元人民幣的點心債，該股今早高開低走，再度失守百元關，中午收報99.55元，跌0.45%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">李寧(02331)早前落實入駐美團閃購，該股昨天與美團齊升，今早亦雙雙回吐。李寧半日跌1.29%，報18.3元，在藍籌中排尾三；尾二是日前遭大和唱淡的石藥(01093)，跌2.19%，報8.03元；表現最差藍籌是理想汽車(02015)，半日跌2.82%，報84.45元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240826_FI_source-web_03690-GW-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240826_FI_source-web_03690-GW-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：美團官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">企業季績持續出爐，有望今日派成績表的藥明康德(02359)偷步造好，早市升2.73%，報109.2元。同樣於今日舉行董事會議決季績的國藥(01099)則逆市跌0.41%，報19.5元；中國海外(00688)也跌0.58%，報13.76元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">昨天收市後派成績表的普拉達(01913)，今年首9個月收益淨額按年升8.9%，所有地區零售均有增長；該股今早收報48.82元，升5.44%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：普拉達2023年度年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240730_FI_source-web_01913-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：普拉達2023年度年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240730_FI_source-web_01913-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：普拉達2023年度年報</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今早共有3家公司獲提私有化或全購後復牌，股價全報揚升。其中五礦地產(00230)獲溢價1.04倍私有化，股價應聲飆91.84%，報0.94元；康大食品(00834)獲溢價16.23%提全購，股價更漲1.59倍，報0.59元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">俊裕地基(01757)獲折讓79.06%提全購，股份今早復牌同樣報升，中午收報0.475元，升11.77%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15367561-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e7%95%a5%e7%b8%ae-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87154%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126122%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e7%a7%91%e8%82%a1%e4%ba%92%e6%9c%89",
